body.body:
Search for matching peptides with the patient specific Ig-V\(D)J-transcriptome \(generated in step A) using the following parameters:
  30.a for MS spectra: Enzyme: Trypsin; Allowed missed cleavages: 1; Fixed modifications: Carbamidomethyl \(C); Variable modifications: Oxidation \(M), \(W); Peptide tolerance: +/- 100 ppm; Mass values: MH+; Monoisotopic;


30.b for MS/MS spectra: Enzyme: Trypsin; Allowed missed cleavages: 1; Fixed modifications: Carbamidomethyl \(C); Variable modifications: Oxidation \(M), \(W); Peptide tolerance: +/- 100 ppm; Peptide charge: 1+; MS/MS tol: +/- 0.8 Da; Monoisotopic; Precursor: mass of interest.
